---
title: Louisiana Beef & Caramelised Onion Pie with Cheesy Potato Topping & Apple Salad
description: This cosy dinner packs a smokey, veggie-loaded beef base full of flavour, then tops off the whole dish with decadent and delicious
gooey Cheddar mashed potatoes. Finishing the meal off under the grill ensures you're eating your tasty creation as fast as possible!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/louisiana-beef-caramelised-onion-pie-dfd3d1e2.jpg
